  "title": "基本 WHERE 子句",
  "group": "SQL 基础",
  "options": [
    {
      "text": "SELECT * FROM users WHERE name LIKE(John);"
    },
    {
      "text": "SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = \""
    },
    {
      "text": "SELECT * FROM users WHERE name == \"John\";"
    },
    {
      "text": "SELECT * FROM users WHERE name === \"John\";"
    }
  ],
  "objectives": [],
  "questionProse": [
    "以下哪个 SQL 查询能正确检索出 name 为 \"John\" 的行？"
  ],
  "questionCode": [],
  "hintsProse": [],
  "hintsCode": [],
  "explanationProse": [
    "在 SQL 中，`WHERE` 子句使用单个等号（`=`）进行相等性检查，而不是 `==` 或 `===`，后者是 JavaScript 运算符。\n\n    正确的语法是 `SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = 'John';`。"
  ],
  "explanationCode": []
}
